From 20b1e3c6ac2204342033b2cbff6e6e9c6b854f83 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 7 Jul 2025 04:18:35 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: DP: Update SDWF TX completion stats

Update SDWF TX and delay statistics during TX completion processing.
Stats are updated either on the primary link or across all links,
depending on whether single-link or multi-link stats collection is
enabled.

All updated statistics are part of the SDWF basic stats set.

Following patch changes are also present
	- 784-02-wifi-ath12k-Add-sawf-tx-stats-support.patch
	- 784-04-ath12k-Add-SAWF-tx-delay-stats-support.patch
	- 786-ath12k-add-per-histogram-count-support.patch
	- 845-wifi-ath12k-Add-SDWF-delay-histogram-stats-support.patch

Signed-off-by: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
